/OS/OS_lab/lab01/output
/.vscode

# --- Logseq Noise Filters ---
# 忽略所有备份文件夹
**/logseq/bak/
**/logseq/.recycle/

# 忽略自动生成的数据库和元数据
**/logseq/.tdb/
**/logseq/metadata.edn

# 不打算在 GitHub 上查看白板索引
**/whiteboards/
# --- GNS3 Lab Filters ---
# Cisco IOS 镜像（专有软件，不应入库）
**/ComputerNetwork/Lab/IOS/
# Dynamips 运行时生成文件（可被 GNS3 自动重建）
**/project-files/dynamips/*/dynamips_*_log.txt
**/project-files/dynamips/*/dynamips_*_stdout.txt
**/project-files/dynamips/*/c3600_*_bootflash
**/project-files/dynamips/*/c3600_*_disk0
**/project-files/dynamips/*/c3600_*_nvram
# VPCS 运行日志
**/project-files/vpcs/*/vpcs.log
